#: ../../platform/usage.rst:7
msgid ""
"All API requests (except login, register, and health check) require a JWT "
"token in the request header:"
msgstr "所有 API 请求（登录、注册和健康检查除外）都需要在请求标头中包含 JWT 令牌："

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:13
msgid "Tokens are valid for 24 hours."
msgstr "令牌的有效期为 24 小时。"

