msgid "Login and Obtain Token"
msgstr "登录并获取令牌"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:40
msgid ""
"``data.access_token`` in the response is the JWT token required for "
"subsequent requests."
msgstr "响应中的 ``data.access_token`` 是后续请求所需的 JWT 令牌。"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:43
msgid "Complete Workflow"
msgstr "完整工作流程"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:45
msgid ""
"The typical workflow is: upload structure file → submit prediction → poll "
"status → download results."
msgstr "典型工作流程为：上传结构文件 → 提交预测 → 轮询状态 → 下载结果。"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:48
msgid "Step 1: Upload Structure Files"
msgstr "第1步：上传结构文件"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:50
msgid ""
"Supports CIF, VASP (POSCAR/CONTCAR), XYZ, PDB, MOL, SDF, JSON, TRAJ, DB "
"formats, as well as ZIP / TAR / TAR.GZ archives."
msgstr ""
"支持CIF、VASP (POSCAR/CONTCAR)、XYZ、PDB、MOL、SDF、JSON、TRAJ、DB格式，以及ZIP / TAR / "
"TAR.GZ档案。"

#: ../../platform/usage.rst:62
msgid ""
"``nx``, ``ny``, ``nz`` are required parameters that specify the three-"
"dimensional grid dimensions for charge density prediction. Grid size "
"directly affects prediction accuracy and computation time; choose "
"appropriate values based on the actual structure."
msgstr "``nx``、``ny``、``nz`` 为必需参数，用于指定电荷密度预测的三维网格维度。网格大小直接影响预测精度与计算时间，请根据实际结构选择合适的值。"

